text.tspan: - origin is mid hip position of estimated pose at t-2
- scaled by diving by approximated person height
- rotated so x-axis points forward and y is aligned
to xy portion of vector from mid hip to left hip at t-2
Features per Node of Graph Data:
from t-2 to every joint from t-1
xt-1 - xt-2 of every joint pair
yt-1 - yt-2 of every joint pair
zt-1 - zt-2 of every joint pair
